# Team Lead Agent — deployment config
# Copy to .env and fill in your values (never commit .env).
#
# Team Lead discovers downstream agents (Jira, UI Design, Web Dev, Code Review)
# via the Capability Registry at runtime. Hardcoded agent URLs are NOT needed
# and should NOT be set here. The only deployment override is the Registry URL
# itself, which comes from config/constellation.yaml (REGISTRY_URL env var).
#
# Non-credential config inherits from config/constellation.yaml.

# ----- OPTIONAL: service binding -----
# HOST=0.0.0.0
# PORT=8030
